{"id":113514,"type":2,"name":"Wish","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1a/49/113514_Bv49v.jpg","rating":{"total":20,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":5,"6":8,"7":7,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.1},"summary":"　　拥有天界最善良纯洁之心的天使琥珀(纯洁得看上去有些笨笨的,还非常爱哭)在人界执行任务时遭到小恶魔红榴欺负,被医生秀一郎所救。为了报恩,琥珀许下实现秀一郎的一个心愿的诺言。可是秀一郎十分,非常,很\"委婉\"的拒绝了：\"心愿是应该由自己完成的\" .。\"人是无法独自生存的,所以一定会有自己一个人不能完成的心愿才对\",所以天使琥珀决定暂留人界,等待报恩的机会。两人的同居生涯于此展开...... 秀一郎终于许下了一个他独自无法实现的心愿：\"希望你能一直留在我身边\"。无法实现的心愿就是...就是...... ","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/39\">CLAMP</a></li><li><span>导演: </span>大川七濑、<a href=\"/person/2172\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">遠藤卓司</a></li><li><span>人物设定: </span><a href=\"/person/36\">阿部恒</a></li><li><span>作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/36\">阿部恒</a></li><li><span>监修: </span><a href=\"/person/912\">りんたろう</a></li><li><span>执行制片人: </span><a href=\"/person/914\">丸山正雄</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/603\">MADHOUSE</a></li><li><span>发售日: </span>1997</li><li><span>片长: </span>5分31秒</li><li><span>IMDb链接: </span>tt0485349</li><li><span>编剧: </span>いがらし寒月</li>","collection":{"wish":22,"collect":34,"doing":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":13},{"name":"CLAMP","count":9},{"name":"1997","count":9},{"name":"MADHouse","count":8},{"name":"短片","count":6},{"name":"漫画改","count":4},{"name":"遠藤卓司","count":1},{"name":"水","count":1},{"name":"95-99","count":1},{"name":"林太郎","count":1},{"name":"1997年","count":1},{"name":"漫改","count":1},{"name":"其他","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":430981,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/430981","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":39,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d6/7d/39_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"CLAMP","desc":"原作"},{"id":2172,"image":"","name":"远藤卓司","desc":"导演"},{"id":36,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/19/ca/36_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"阿部恒","desc":"人物设定"},{"id":912,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2a/9d/912_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"林重行","desc":"监修